ूतानि पर्जन्यादन्नसम्भवः ।\u003cbr/\u003eयज्ञा‍द्भ‍‍वति पर्जन्यो यज्ञः कर्मसमुद्भ‍वः ॥ १४ ॥\"}]},{\"section\":\"verse_text\",\"section_title\":\"Books.Verse.verse-text\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"content.Record\",\"title\":\"verse_text\",\"id\":1062,\"bb\":948,\"url_path\":\"/en/library/bg/3/14/b948/\",\"body_value\":\"\u003cem\u003eannād bhavanti bhūtāni\u003cbr /\u003eparjanyād anna-sambhavaḥ\u003cbr /\u003eyajñād bhavati parjanyo\u003cbr /\u003eyajñaḥ karma-samudbhavaḥ\u003c/em\u003e\"}]},{\"section\":\"synonyms\",\"section_title\":\"Books.Verse.synonyms\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"books.Synonyms\",\"title\":\"synonyms\",\"id\":1063,\"bb\":949,\"url_path\":\"/en/library/bg/3/14/b949/\",\"shadow_value\":\"\u003cem\u003eannāt\u003c/em\u003e – from grains; \u003cem\u003ebhavanti\u003c/em\u003e – grow; \u003cem\u003ebhūtāni\u003c/em\u003e – the material bodies; \u003cem\u003eparjanyāt\u003c/em\u003e – from rains; \u003cem\u003eanna\u003c/em\u003e – of food grains; \u003cem\u003esambhavaḥ\u003c/em\u003e – production; \u003cem\u003eyajñāt\u003c/em\u003e – from the performance of sacrifice; \u003cem\u003ebhavati\u003c/em\u003e – becomes possible; \u003cem\u003eparjanyaḥ\u003c/em\u003e – rain; \u003cem\u003eyajñaḥ\u003c/em\u003e – performance of \u003cem\u003eyajña;\u003c/em\u003e \u003cem\u003ekarma\u003c/em\u003e – prescribed duties; \u003cem\u003esamudbhavaḥ\u003c/em\u003e – born of.\",\"word_for_word_value\":[{\"word\":\"annāt\",\"translation\":\"from grains\"},{\"word\":\"bhavanti\",\"translation\":\"grow\"},{\"word\":\"bhūtāni\",\"translation\":\"the material bodies\"},{\"word\":\"parjanyāt\",\"translation\":\"from rains\"},{\"word\":\"anna\",\"translation\":\"of food grains\"},{\"word\":\"sambhavaḥ\",\"translation\":\"production\"},{\"word\":\"yajñāt\",\"translation\":\"from the performance of sacrifice\"},{\"word\":\"bhavati\",\"translation\":\"becomes possible\"},{\"word\":\"parjanyaḥ\",\"translation\":\"rain\"},{\"word\":\"yajñaḥ\",\"translation\":\"performance