m. His potencies are multifarious, and thus His deeds are automatically performed as a natural sequence.”\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c/strong\u003e(\u003cem\u003eŚvetāśvatara Upaniṣad\u003c/em\u003e 6.7–8)\"},{\"type\":\"content.Record\",\"title\":\"paragraph\",\"id\":1120,\"bb\":998,\"url_path\":\"/en/library/bg/3/22/b998/\",\"body_value\":\"Since everything is in full opulence in the Personality of Godhead and is existing in full truth, there is no duty for the Supreme Personality of Godhead to perform. One who must receive the results of work has some designated duty, but one who has nothing to achieve within the three planetary systems certainly has no duty. And yet Lord Kṛṣṇa is engaged on the Battlefield of Kurukṣetra as the leader of the \u003cem\u003ekṣatriyas\u003c/em\u003e because the \u003cem\u003ekṣatriyas\u003c/em\u003e are duty-bound to give protection to the distressed. Although He is above all the regulations of the revealed scriptures, He does not do anything that violates the revealed scriptures.\"}]}],\"short_title\":\"Bg. 3.22\",\"medium_title\":\"Bhagavad-gītā As It Is 3.22\"},{\"id\":1121,\"meta\":{\"type\":\"books.Verse\",\"slug\":\"23\",\"show_in_menus\":false,\"seo_title\":\"\",\"search_description\":\"\",\"first_published_at\":null,\"alias_of\":null,\"locale\":\"en\"},\"title\":\"TEXT 23\",\"advanced_view_url_path\":\"/en/library/bg/3/advanced-view/#bb999\",\"language_menu\":[{\"display_name\":\"አማርኛ (Ethiopian)\",\"language_code\":\"am\",\"enabled\":false,\"url_path\":\"/am/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Български (Bulgarian)\",\"language_code\":\"bg\",\"enabled\":true,\"url_path\":\"/bg/library/bg/3/23/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Čeština (Czech)\",\"language_code\":\"cs\",\"enabled\":true,\"url_path\":\"/cs/library/bg/3/23/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Dansk (Danish)\",\"language_code\":\"da\",\"enabled\":true,\"url_path\":\"/da/library/bg/3/23/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Deutsch (German)\",\"language_code\":\"de\",\"enabled\":true,\"url_path\":\"/de/library/bg/3