 and evil work have their reactions, and any reaction binds the performer. Therefore, one has to work in Kṛṣṇa consciousness to satisfy Kṛṣṇa (or Viṣṇu); and while performing such activities one is in a liberated stage. This is the great art of doing work, and in the beginning this process requires very expert guidance. One should therefore act very diligently, under the expert guidance of a devotee of Lord Kṛṣṇa, or under the direct instruction of Lord Kṛṣṇa Himself (under whom Arjuna had the opportunity to work). Nothing should be performed for sense gratification, but everything should be done for the satisfaction of Kṛṣṇa. This practice will not only save one from the reaction of work, but also gradually elevate one to transcendental loving service of the Lord, which alone can raise one to the kingdom of God.\"}}]}]]]}]\n"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"78:[\"$\",\"div\",\"1030-devanagari,1030-devanagari\",{\"className\":\"av-devanagari\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-center em:leading-5 em:text-xl font-bold em:mb-4 hidden\",\"children\":\"Devanagari\"}],[[\"$\",\"$L4a\",\"child-1031\",{\"child\":\"$2b:props:children:0:props:children:props:page:child_items:0:children:9:child_items:0:children:0\",\"hasId\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"em:mb-4 em:leading-8 em:text-lg text-center\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"सहयज्ञाः प्रजाः सृष्ट्वा पुरोवाच प्रजापतिः ।\u003cbr/\u003eअनेन प्रसविष्यध्वमेष वोऽस्त्विष्टकामधुक् ॥ १० ॥\"}}]}]]]}]\n79:[\"$\",\"div\",\"1030-verse_text,1030-verse_text\",{\"className\":\"av-verse_text\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-center em:leading-5 em:text-xl font-bold em:mb-4 hidden\",\"children\":\"Verse text\"}],[[\"$\",\"$L4a\",\"child-1032\",{\"child\":\"$2b:props:children:0:props:children:props:page:child_items:0:children:9:child_items:1:children:0\",\"hasId\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"em:mb-4 em:leading-8 em:text-base t