s teaching should be based on the principles of such standard \u003cem\u003eśāstras.\u003c/em\u003e One who desires to improve himself must follow the standard rules as they are practiced by the great teachers. The \u003cem\u003eŚrīmad-Bhāgavatam\u003c/em\u003e also affirms that one should follow in the footsteps of great devotees, and that is the way of progress on the path of spiritual realization. The king or the executive head of a state, the father and the schoolteacher are all considered to be natural leaders of the innocent people in general. All such natural leaders have a great responsibility to their dependents; therefore they must be conversant with standard books of moral and spiritual codes.b3:[\"$\",\"div\",\"1104-purport,1104-purport"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\",{\"className\":\"av-purport\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-center em:leading-5 em:text-xl font-bold em:mb-4\",\"children\":\"Purport\"}],[[\"$\",\"$L4a\",\"child-1109\",{\"child\":\"$2b:props:children:0:props:children:props:page:child_items:0:children:20:child_items:4:children:0\",\"hasId\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"em:mb-4 em:leading-8 em:text-base s-justify\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$130\"}}]}]]]}]\nb4:[\"$\",\"div\",\"1110-devanagari,1110-devanagari\",{\"className\":\"av-devanagari\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-center em:leading-5 em:text-xl font-bold em:mb-4 hidden\",\"children\":\"Devanagari\"}],[[\"$\",\"$L4a\",\"child-1111\",{\"child\":\"$2b:props:children:0:props:children:props:page:child_items:0:children:21:child_items:0:children:0\",\"hasId\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"em:mb-4 em:leading-8 em:text-lg text-center\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"न मे पार्थास्ति कर्तव्यं त्रिषु लोकेषु किञ्चन ।\u003cbr/\u003eनानवाप्त‍मवाप्त‍व्यं वर्त एव च कर्मणि ॥ २२ ॥\"}}]}]]]}]\nb5:[\"$\",\"div\",\"1110-verse_text,1110-verse_text\",{\"className\":\"