an, but if any common man tries to drink even a fragment of such poison, he will be killed. There are many pseudo devotees of Lord Śiva who want to indulge in smoking \u003cem\u003egañjā\u003c/em\u003e (marijuana) and similar intoxicating drugs, forgetting that by so imitating the acts of Lord Śiva they are calling death very near. Similarly, there are some pseudo devotees of Lord Kṛṣṇa who prefer to imitate the Lord in His \u003cem\u003erāsa-līlā,\u003c/em\u003e or dance of love, forgetting their inability to lift Govardhana Hill. It is best, therefore, that one not try to imitate the powerful, but simply follow their instructions; nor should one try to occupy their posts without qualification. There are so many “incarnations” of God without the power of the Supreme Godhead."])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"c2:[\"$\",\"div\",\"1127-purport,1127-purport\",{\"className\":\"av-purport\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-center em:leading-5 em:text-xl font-bold em:mb-4\",\"children\":\"Purport\"}],[[\"$\",\"$L4a\",\"child-1132\",{\"child\":\"$2b:props:children:0:props:children:props:page:child_items:0:children:23:child_items:4:children:0\",\"hasId\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"em:mb-4 em:leading-8 em:text-base s-justify\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$131\"}}]}],[\"$\",\"$L4a\",\"child-1133\",{\"child\":\"$2b:props:children:0:props:children:props:page:child_items:0:children:23:child_items:4:children:1\",\"hasId\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"em:mb-4 em:leading-8 em:text-base text-center italic\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"\u003cem\u003enaitat samācarej jātu\u003cbr /\u003emanasāpi hy anīśvaraḥ\u003cbr /\u003evinaśyaty ācaran mauḍhyād\u003cbr /\u003eyathārudro ’bdhi-jaṁ viṣam\u003c/em\u003e\"}}]}],[\"$\",\"$L4a\",\"child-1134\",{\"child\":\"$2b:props:children:0:props:children:props:page:child_items:0:children:23:child_items:4:children:2\",\"hasId\":true,\"child